name: Shadowbat
description:
Entered via: Shadow rift #20211219
Power level: Creeper
Size:  6.6 feet/ 1.98 meters tall
Aspect: Darkness
Secondary Aspects: None

Shadowbats are lithe, terrifying, Darkness-aligned flying creatures that teleport through shadows to ambush their prey. These snake-like, winged demons love to emerge from the deepest shadows, snatch their prey, and then pull them back to a safer location. 

While their mobility makes Shadowbats dangerous foes, they have the strength of an average human, as well as soft, fleshy skin, so the chances of being able to fight one off if captured is much higher than most other demons thus the designation of Creeper level.
